"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CL-3_Part_AMPM_System-WebImage-VERT-v4-2.jpg","image_height_mobile":"adapt","content_position_mobile":"items-end justify-start","text_alignment_mobile":"left","color_text":"#ffffff","color_highlight":"#e0a580","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"#171717","color_button_background":"#ffffff","color_button_gradient":"","color_overlay":"#171717","overlay_opacity":70,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"divider":false,"full_width":true,"rounded":false,"enable_parallax":false,"parallax_direction":"vertical"}},"product_details_HtPqrn":{"type":"product-details","blocks":{"collapsible_tab_Kj8kyV":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"icon":"lightning","icon_width":24,"heading":"Energy Levels","content":"<p>Coastline supports energy systems where they start. <strong>Creatine<\/strong>, <strong>Taurine<\/strong>, and <strong>Magnesium<\/strong> drive ATP recycling, while <strong>CoQ10<\/strong> and <strong>Ergothioneine<\/strong> optimize mitochondrial output and shield cells from burnout. Combined with <strong>Inulin<\/strong> for glucose stability, our 13-ingredient clinically-dosed system delivers stable, holistic energy that lasts.<\/p>","metafields":""}},"collapsible_tab_LP3aKi":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"icon":"star","icon_width":24,"heading":"Brain Support","content":"<p>Coastline supports your mind for demanding days and deep recovery. <strong>Ergothioneine, Taurine, and Creatine<\/strong> fortify cognition under stress, while <strong>L-theanine<\/strong> and <strong>Magnesium Citrate<\/strong> sharpen focus and support neurotransmission. With <strong>micro-dosed Lithium<\/strong> for mood regulation and long-term durability, our system ensures you stay composed when you need to perform and relaxed when it’s time to wind down.<\/p>","metafields":""}},"collapsible_tab_9HpFgD":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"icon":"wrench","icon_width":24,"heading":"Muscles, Bones, & Joints","content":"<p>Coastline supports your physical foundation and peak performance through every stage of life.<strong> Creatine<\/strong> and <strong>Taurine<\/strong> drive muscle strength and endurance, while <strong>Glycine<\/strong> and <strong>Glucosamine<\/strong> preserve collagen and cartilage integrity. By pairing these with <strong>Magnesium Citrate<\/strong> to optimize nutrient utilization, our system helps you stay physically capable, active, and resilient.<\/p>","metafields":""}},"collapsible_tab_EiadYp":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"icon":"heart","icon_width":24,"heading":"Cardio-metabolic Support","content":"<p><strong>Taurine, Magnesium Citrate <\/strong>and<strong> Inulin<\/strong> have each been shown to help improve blood pressure, glucose handling and lipid markers. <strong>CoQ10 <\/strong>supports vascular function, while <strong>Astaxanthin<\/strong> helps protect against oxidative stress that injures vessels over time. Coastline is designed to reduce silent risk — not just fix what you can feel.<\/p>","metafields":""}},"collapsible_tab_6a9xdt":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"icon":"shield","icon_width":24,"heading":"Cellular Protection & Healthy Aging","content":"<p>Coastline supports your biological longevity by protecting at the cellular level. <strong>Ergothioneine, Astaxanthin, and CoQ10<\/strong> defend against oxidative and mitochondrial stress, while <strong>Lutein<\/strong> and <strong>Zeaxanthin<\/strong> provide systemic protection. With <strong>Glycine, Taurine, and Inulin<\/strong> to support inflammation control and gut-immune balance, our 13-ingredient system targets the hallmarks of aging to support overall health as you age. <\/p>","metafields":""}}},"block_order":["collapsible_tab_Kj8kyV","collapsible_tab_LP3aKi","collapsible_tab_9HpFgD","collapsible_tab_EiadYp","collapsible_tab_6a9xdt"],"custom_css":[],"name":"Benefits Accordian NEW","settings":{"style":"with-border","open_first_row":false,"specifications_heading":"","heading":"Supports All 11 Body Syste