benefits include:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Brain & Cognition<\/li><li>Metabolic & Glucose Control<\/li><li>Muscle, Bone & Mobility<\/li><li>Inflammation & Immune Modulation<\/li><li>Gut & Microbiome Health<\/li><li>Mitochondrial Function & Cellular Energy<\/li><li>Proteostasis & Cellular Cleanup <\/li><li>Stress, Mood & Sleep Resilience<\/li><\/ul>","page":"","liquid":""}},"collapsible_tab_yArwfT":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"When & How to Take","content":"<p>Take the <strong>morning blend and softgels with your first meal<\/strong> — this step is built to support daytime energy, cognition, metabolic control, and physical function while you’re “on.” Later in the day or with dinner, take the <strong>evening capsules<\/strong> — this step is designed to support recovery, calm, anti-inflammatory repair, and overnight cellular cleanup while you sleep. No cycling or special rules required. Just water, daily consistency, repeat.<\/p>","page":"","liquid":""}},"collapsible_tab_tTKrBr":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"About Coastline","content":"<p>Coastline was built for people who want to stay sharp, strong, and steady while life is full — especially busy parents burning the candle at both ends. Longevity has become a confusing mix of miracle claims or 80-ingredient kitchen-sink blends with no rationale. Coastline takes the third path: only ingredients with human-relevant evidence, dosed at levels used in trials, arranged into a simple morning–evening rhythm you can actually live with. Instead of chasing hype or “one magic pill,” Coastline was engineered to target the biology that matters most for modern aging — cognition, metabolic control, inflammation, mitochondrial function, and physical resilience. One system that actually moves the biology that matters — without making your life harder to run.<\/p>","page":"","liquid":""}}},"block_order":["liquid_CMnYHh","title_4Kgce3","description_raF6BU","variant_picker_D