Cfc9f","feature_kf3PqM","feature_QRbw7e"],"name":"multi-icon-mobile","settings":{"background_color":"#f7f7f7","card_background":"#f7f7f7","icon_color":"#062f3d","title_color":"#062f3d","description_color":"#006580","icon_size":20,"title_size":12,"description_size":12}},"multicolumn_wnTQAt":{"type":"multicolumn","blocks":{"column_WaEYXw":{"type":"column","settings":{"show_border":false,"text_alignment":"left","text_alignment_mobile":"left","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Greg_Portrait.webp","image_ratio":"portrait","heading":"<em>\"The 13 ingredients chosen for Coastline are the most scientifically supported, and clinically validated supplements yet to be discovered.\"<\/em>","heading_size":"text-lg-2xl","text":"<p>\"After reviewing thousands of research papers and analyzing countless supplement protocols, these 13 ingredients represent the gold standard. Each one has robust clinical evidence and addresses fundamental aspects of healthy aging that I see compromised in my practice every day.\"<br\/><br\/><strong>– Greg Potter, PhD, MSc<\/strong><br\/><em>Sleep & Circadian Health Researcher<\/em><\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"column_bprWzp":{"type":"column","settings":{"show_border":false,"text_alignment":"left","text_alignment_mobile":"left","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Jessicabodasphotography-jacques.webp","image_ratio":"portrait","heading":"<em><strong>\"Coastline is what happens when you combine scientific rigor with real-world clinical understanding.\"<\/strong><\/em>","heading_size":"text-lg-2xl","text":"<p>\"After over two decades working in the clinical nutrition industry, I’ve seen how confusing the supplement landscape can be. Coastline takes a strictly evidence-driven approach, with clinically meaningful doses, and clear intent behind every inclusion. It’s a formulation built not to follow trends, but to stand the test of time.<\/p><p><strong> – Dr. Jacqueline Jacques, ND<\/strong><br\/><em>Doctor of Naturopathic Medicine<br\/>Wellness Industry Expert<\/em><\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"column_cpnFbB":{"type":"column","settings":{"show_border":false,"text_alignment":"left","text_alignment_mobile":"left","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Nic_Portrait.webp","image_ratio":"portrait","heading":"<em><strong>\"I value Coastline's quality, and scientifically rigorous ingredients. It means less hassle with the greatest certainty of results.\"<\/strong><\/em>","heading_size":"text-lg-2xl","text":"<p>\"The foundational supplements found in Coastline are all noticeably effective as determined by, primarily, human trials, and are dosed appropriately. Additionally, Coastline combines this highly curated stack into one simple supplement matrix that hits all aspects of healthspan. <br\/><br\/><strong>– Dr. Nicolas Verhoeven<\/strong><br\/><em>Ph.D. in Molecular Medicine, M.S. Kinesiology - Exercise PhysiologyACSM CPT<\/em><\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"column_CCqnEB":{"type":"column","settings":{"show_border":false,"text_alignment":"left","text_alignment_mobile":"left","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CL-ChrisP-Scientist.webp","image_ratio":"portrait","heading":"<em>\"Coastline represents a new era of precision supplementation — one rooted in clarity, science, and consistency.\"<\/em>","heading_size":"text-lg-2xl","text":"<p>\"Most supplements are built around marketing stories rather than measurable outcomes. Coastline has stripped away that noise to focus only on ingredients with real data behind them — that directly influence the pathways of cellular health, recovery, and longevity For me, that’s the future: fewer ingredients, more certainty, and an evidence-based foundation people can trust every single day.\"<br\/><br\/><strong>– Dr. Chris Pollock, PhD<\/strong><\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["column_WaEYXw","column_bprWzp","column_cpnFbB","column_CCqnEB"],"custom_css":[],"name":"Scientist Scroller","settings":{"gap":"large","columns":4,"columns_mobile":"1","swipe_on_mobile":true,"heading":"Meet The Experts Behind Coastline","heading_size":"title-lg tracking-heading","heading_alignment":"text-left md:items-end md:flex-row","heading_tag":"h2","subheading":"","description":"<p>Accredited Doctors, nutritionists, and PhDs from around the world all recognize the excellence of Coastline's approach & formulation.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","color_text":"","color_background":"#a3c7d0","gradient_background":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":48,"padding_bottom":20,"divider":false,"full_width":false,"rounded":false}},"rich_text_ahywUW":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_e7jqQt":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>The product reviews reflect individual experiences, and as individuals vary, so may results. To support and complement benefits, it is important to prioritize healthy lifestyle choices, including consistent exercise, a balanced diet, ample rest, and mindfulness. Use as directed.<\/em><\/p>","text_size":"subtext-sm","text_max_size":12,"text_font":"body","secondary_color":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["text_e7jqQt"],"disabled":true,"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"text_alignment":"center","text_alignment_mobile":"center","heading":"","heading_size":"title-md","heading_alignment":"text-left md:items-end md:flex-row","heading_width":"small","heading_tag":"h2","subheading":"","description":"","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","color_text":"#f7f7f7","color_background":"#062f3d","gradient_background":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":64,"divider":false,"narrow":true,"rounded":false}},"image_with_text_CRg9YM":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_z3HUtF":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Free Gift With Welcome Pack","heading_size":"title-lg tracking-heading","heading_tag":"h2","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"text_XAmfBg":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>Receive a FREE Glass Shaker with your Coastline Welcome Pack. ($15 Value) <\/em><\/p>","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"text_font":"body","secondary_color":false,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"button_dtyfKr":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"BUY NOW","button_link":"#shopify-section-template--18536556888133__featured_product_wcLyNe","button_size":"md","button_external":false,"button_icon":false,"button_secondary_style":false}}},"block_order":["heading_z3HUtF","text_XAmfBg","button_dtyfKr"],"custom_css":["\/* Button *\/.button--primary.icon-with-text,.button--primary.icon-with-text:hover,.button--primary.icon-with-text:active,.button--primary.icon-with-text::after,.button--primary.icon-with-text:active::after {border-radius: 10px !important;}",".button--primary.icon-with-text {margin-top: 30px; padding: 15px 100px;}"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/WATERBOTTLE.jpg","image_height":"650px","image_width":"medium","layout":"text_first","text_alignment":"left","content_position":"align-self-center","image_height_mobile":"auto","text_alignment_mobile":"left","color_text":"","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_background_2":"","gradient_background_2":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"#062f3d","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":72,"padding_bottom":72,"divider":false,"full_width":false,"rounded":false,"enable_parallax":true,"parallax_direction":"vertical"}},"faq_64f36A":{"type":"faq","blocks":{"question_UMdW7G":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"When will I notice results?","text":"<p>Most members report feeling more consistent energy within the first week, with sleep quality improvements often noticed within 3-5 days. More significant benefits like improved recovery and sustained vitality typically develop over 4-8 weeks of consistent use as your body reaches optimal nutrient levels.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_NMRfUD":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"How is Coastline different from other supplements?","text":"<p>Coastline is a complete AM\/PM system targeting 11 body systems and 12 hallmarks of aging, not just isolated nutrients. We use research-backed dosages, third-party testing, and transparent labeling. No proprietary blends, artificial flavors, or under-dosed ingredients common in other products.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_7n7H8R":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Can I take Coastline with my current supplements?","text":"<p>Coastline is designed as a comprehensive foundation, potentially replacing multiple individual supplements. However, we recommend consulting your healthcare provider before making changes to your current regimen, especially if you take medications or have health conditions.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_PgqVpU":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"What is your subscription policy?","text":"<p>You're in complete control. Pause, skip, or cancel anytime through your account dashboard. No contracts, hidden fees, or cancellation hassles. We'll always show your next charge date and send reminders before processing orders. Plus we have a 60-day money back guarantee - so you sign up completely risk free. <\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_76M9dY":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"How do you take Coastline?","text":"<p>Take the Morning Blend and SoftGels with breakfast and the Evening Capsules ideally 1-hour before bed. This timing supports natural circadian rhythms and optimizes absorption. Each step is clearly labeled and contains the optimal daily dose.<\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"question_nDJmGf":{"type":"question","settings":{"title":"Are there any side effects?","text":"<p>Coastline uses ingredients at nutritional doses with excellent safety profiles. Some people may experience mild digestive changes initially as your gut gets a significant upgrade. In this case we recommend starting with a half measure of the morning blend powder for the first week, and then moving to a full scoop thereafter. <\/p>","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"contact_FhBA8M":{"type":"contact","settings":{"heading":"Didn’t find your answer?","text":"<p>Don't hestitate to contact us<\/p>","show_phone":false,"avatar_height":60,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["question_UMdW7G","question_NMRfUD","question_7n7H8R","question_PgqVpU","question_76M9dY","question_nDJmGf","contact_FhBA8M"],"custom_css":[],"name":"t:sections.faq.presets.name","settings":{"style":"with-border","heading":"Most Common Questions:","heading_size":"title-md","heading_alignment":"text-left md:items-end md:flex-row","heading_tag":"h2","subheading":"","description":"","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","color_text":"#f7f7